            <span>Bienvenido! Soy Carlos Puga </span>
            <Badge
              class="transition-all duration-300 scale-100 hover:scale-110 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-emerald-400/40 hover:bg-emerald-500/10"
              >Open to work</Badge
            >
          </h1>
          <h2
            class="text-lg sm:text-xl opacity-70 pb-4 text-center sm:text-left">
            Ingeniero en conectividad y redes / Full Stack developer.
          </h2>
          <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center sm:justify-start">
            <Socials href="https://www.linkedin.com">
              <LinkedInIcon class="size-5" /> LinkedIn
            </Socials>
            <Socials href="https://github.com">
              <GithubIcon class="size-5" /> Github
            </Socials>
            <Socials href="mailto:CarlosPuga.Sa@gmail.com">
